{
    "publish_date": "2013-07-17T14:17:23.000Z", 
    "score": 1.5472570999760177e-05, 
    "video_length": "PT8M8S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE]", 
            "dur": "2.666", 
            "start": "0"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "LARRY KOSILLA: Larry here\nfrom ammonyc.com.", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "2.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, the detailing industry has\nevolved drastically over", 
            "dur": "2.83", 
            "start": "5.106"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the past few years.", 
            "dur": "1.35", 
            "start": "7.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Today, manufacturers are\ndesigning high tech tools and", 
            "dur": "2.43", 
            "start": "9.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "products that allow detailers to\ncreate perfect works of art", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "11.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in a way that&#39;s much safer and\neasier than ever before.", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "14.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In today&#39;s episode I&#39;ll walk you\nthrough my top five tools", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "17.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that have changed the detailing\nindustry forever.", 
            "dur": "2.698", 
            "start": "20.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "23.422", 
            "start": "23.024"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So here we go.", 
            "dur": "1.03", 
            "start": "46.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Number five on my top\nfive list is the", 
            "dur": "1.89", 
            "start": "47.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "microfiber cutting pad.", 
            "dur": "1.63", 
            "start": "49.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This tool virtually eliminates\nthe need for aggressive wool", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "50.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or foam cutting pads\non a rotary.", 
            "dur": "1.51", 
            "start": "53.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now the rotary and wool pads are\nstill a staple in the body", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "55.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "shop industry for heavy wet\nsand removal, but as a", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "57.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "detailer, these pads allow you\nthe ability to correct major", 
            "dur": "2.85", 
            "start": "60.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "paint defects with a dual action\ntype polisher, which", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "63.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was never possible before.", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "65.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let&#39;s take a closer look\nat the pads themselves.", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "67.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Microfiber pads can differ in a\nfew ways including the type", 
            "dur": "3.93", 
            "start": "70.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of foam backing, the actual\nmicrofiber material, and the", 
            "dur": "4.02", 
            "start": "73.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "length of the pile itself.", 
            "dur": "2.45", 
            "start": "77.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Most backings are either open\ncell or closed cell foams with", 
            "dur": "4.12", 
            "start": "80.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "varying degrees of depth.", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "84.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Closed cell backing--", 
            "dur": "1.17", 
            "start": "86.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "seen here--", 
            "dur": "1.09", 
            "start": "87.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have a much tighter, or stiffer\nfoam composition,", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "88.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which transfers the power of\nthe machine quickly to the", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "91.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "microfiber pile, and it&#39;s\ngreat on hard paints.", 
            "dur": "4.16", 
            "start": "94.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Open cell backing allows for\ngreater airflow because the", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "98.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pores are larger and can absorb\nthe power and heat,", 
            "dur": "3.29", 
            "start": "102.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "making them safe and\neasy to use,", 
            "dur": "1.95", 
            "start": "105.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "especially on soft paints.", 
            "dur": "1.84", 
            "start": "107.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The most recent variations\ninclude pile height and a wide", 
            "dur": "3.54", 
            "start": "109.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "range of foam packing depths\nthat manipulate the transfer", 
            "dur": "3.42", 
            "start": "112.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of power from the machine to\nthe paint based on the", 
            "dur": "3.15", 
            "start": "116.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "combination of the pad&#39;s\nmaterial, its overall size,", 
            "dur": "3.3", 
            "start": "119.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "plus its depth.", 
            "dur": "1.73", 
            "start": "122.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These are some things\nto think about when", 
            "dur": "1.569", 
            "start": "124.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re choosing a pad.", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "125.905"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I get so excited about this\ntool because it almost", 
            "dur": "2.561", 
            "start": "127.375"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "completely negates years of\nlearning how to safely operate", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "129.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a rotary machine.", 
            "dur": "1.2", 
            "start": "132.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now you can use a dual action\npolisher and get an even", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "134.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "better, swirl free\npaint correction.", 
            "dur": "2.41", 
            "start": "136.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Number four should be no\nsurprise to anyone because", 
            "dur": "2.09", 
            "start": "138.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we&#39;re talking about automotive\nclay bars.", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "140.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, the first form of clay\nwas used in a body shop in", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "142.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Japan in the 1980s to remove\noverspray without having to", 
            "dur": "3.09", 
            "start": "145.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "compound the paint.", 
            "dur": "1.33", 
            "start": "148.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Soon after, we realized it&#39;s not\nonly good for overspray,", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "149.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but for metal shavings from\nbrake dust, road dust, and", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "152.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "environmental fallout.", 
            "dur": "0.945", 
            "start": "155.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It has since been adapted to\nmicrofiber towels, and even to", 
            "dur": "3.275", 
            "start": "156.101"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pads designed for dual\naction polishers.", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "159.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Clay is very sticky, and without\nlubrication, it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.46", 
            "start": "162.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "impossible to use effectively.", 
            "dur": "1.95", 
            "start": "164.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After your car&#39;s been washed,\nuse spray wax, clay lube, or", 
            "dur": "3.2", 
            "start": "166.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "car soap and water\nas lubrication.", 
            "dur": "2.45", 
            "start": "169.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Clay works by friction,\nnot pressure.", 
            "dur": "2.17", 
            "start": "172.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what that means is you want\nto move your hand in quick", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "174.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "back and forth motions,\nnot by pushing hard.", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "176.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The clay&#39;s stickiness pulls the\nembedded contaminants from", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "179.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the surface of the paint,\nleaving a smooth surface.", 
            "dur": "2.63", 
            "start": "181.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Be sure to use plenty\nof lubrication when", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "184.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "using a clay bar.", 
            "dur": "1.67", 
            "start": "186.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In this example, I&#39;m using spray\nwax because I&#39;m only", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "188.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "working an isolated area\nof paint contamination.", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "191.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "However, if I was claying the\nentire vehicle, I would use", 
            "dur": "3.28", 
            "start": "194.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the foam, or suds, after a wash\nto save product, time,", 
            "dur": "4.26", 
            "start": "197.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and, of course, money.", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "201.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Work the clay in straight lines\nwith light pressure and", 
            "dur": "3.04", 
            "start": "203.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "quick arm motions.", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "206.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The contaminants in the\npaint will now be", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "209.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "embedded in the clay.", 
            "dur": "1.62", 
            "start": "211.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After one or two panels, or when\nthe clay becomes full,", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "212.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "twist or knead the material\nuntil a fresh area is exposed.", 
            "dur": "4.08", 
            "start": "215.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Flatten into a hamburger\nshape, and continue.", 
            "dur": "3.59", 
            "start": "219.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And remember, if the bar happens\nto fall on the floor,", 
            "dur": "3.02", 
            "start": "223.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "throw it away immediately.", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "226.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My third favorite tool\nis coatings.", 
            "dur": "2.27", 
            "start": "228.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In the last four to five years,\nchemistry has allowed", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "231.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "us to create products with\nunique chemical resistant", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "233.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "properties referred\nto as coatings.", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "235.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These liquids are extremely\nhydrophobic and adhere to the", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "238.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "clear coat to help protect\nthe material beneath it.", 
            "dur": "2.66", 
            "start": "240.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Some coatings can be tricky to\ninstall, and will require", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "243.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "adequate time for drying or\ncuring before removal.", 
            "dur": "3.24", 
            "start": "246.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Coatings are great as the\nfoundation, or last line of", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "249.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "defense, when protecting your\npaint, especially when paint", 
            "dur": "2.865", 
            "start": "252.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sealants and waxes are\nlayered on top.", 
            "dur": "2.395", 
            "start": "255.061"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A common misconception is that\nonce a coating is applied,", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "257.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "regular maintenance of properly\nwashing, drying,", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "260.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sealing, and waxing your car\nis unnecessary, and that&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.81", 
            "start": "262.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just not true.", 
            "dur": "0.9", 
            "start": "265.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Coatings are not magic potions\nthat solve all of your car", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "266.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "care needs.", 
            "dur": "0.89", 
            "start": "269.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They are however, a fantastic\naddition to the team of", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "270.106"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "products used to protect the\ndepth and shine of your car&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.8", 
            "start": "272.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "finish, especially in today&#39;s\nharsh environment.", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "275.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Coatings should be applied\ndirectly to the", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "278.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "surface of the paint.", 
            "dur": "1.23", 
            "start": "280.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So washing with dish soap, or\nwiping with isopropanol might", 
            "dur": "3.59", 
            "start": "281.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "be necessary based on the\ncurrent condition of your car.", 
            "dur": "4.13", 
            "start": "285.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Apply the coating evenly, and\nmake sure to read the", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "289.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "directions for cure times\nand removal procedures.", 
            "dur": "3.67", 
            "start": "291.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Once installed and properly\ncured, add paint sealant then", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "295.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wax for a warm, deep glow, and\nto protect the coating itself.", 
            "dur": "5.37", 
            "start": "298.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The next item was chosen because\nit drastically shrunk", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "304.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the learning curve when\npolishing your paint.", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "306.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And of course, I&#39;m\ntalking about", 
            "dur": "1.38", 
            "start": "308.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the dual action polisher.", 
            "dur": "1.53", 
            "start": "309.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These machines have bridged the\ngap between professional", 
            "dur": "2.4", 
            "start": "311.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "detailers and weekend\nwarriors.", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "313.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Rotary polishers were once\nthought of as the go to", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "315.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "machine for paint restoration,\nbut are now somewhat", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "318.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "antiquated within\nthe industry.", 
            "dur": "1.88", 
            "start": "320.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The latest version of polishers\nincorporate power", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "322.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and speed of a rotary with the\nsafety and ease of the basic", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "324.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "DA machine.", 
            "dur": "1.39", 
            "start": "327.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There are many different dual\naction polishers available", 
            "dur": "2.83", 
            "start": "329.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that vary in power, weight,\nrotation, and", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "332.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even orbital throw.", 
            "dur": "1.4", 
            "start": "335.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But whichever DA you&#39;re\ncomfortable with, microfiber", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "336.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "cutting pads are vital to it&#39;s\npaint correcting capabilities.", 
            "dur": "4.34", 
            "start": "339.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If I had to predict the next\nadvancement in polishers, it", 
            "dur": "2.36", 
            "start": "343.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would be the combination of dual\naction, forced rotation,", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "345.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with the throw of 15\nto 20 millimeters.", 
            "dur": "2.55", 
            "start": "348.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Only time will tell, but I can&#39;t\nwait to see what&#39;s next.", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "351.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My number one item that&#39;s\nchanged the detailing industry", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "354.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is something that you may have\noverlooked because it&#39;s so", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "357.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "common and integrated into\nthe detailing community.", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "359.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;m talking about\nmicrofiber towels.", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "362.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Microfiber is a synthetic\nmaterial made from the", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "364.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "combination of polyester\nand polymide.", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "366.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s appropriately named because\nthe fibers are roughly", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "368.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "1/60 the size of a human\nhair, making it", 
            "dur": "2.82", 
            "start": "371.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "finer than most silks.", 
            "dur": "1.68", 
            "start": "374.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Although microfiber dates back\nto the late 1970s, and was", 
            "dur": "3.33", 
            "start": "375.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "originally used for clothing and\nthe textile industries, it", 
            "dur": "3.23", 
            "start": "379.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wasn&#39;t until the early 2000s\nthat this material was", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "382.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "marketed to the car\ncleaning industry.", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "385.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And its impact on the detailing\ncommunity can&#39;t be", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "387.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "overstated.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "390.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I believe this to be\nthe best product", 
            "dur": "1.35", 
            "start": "391.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "advancement for a few reasons.", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "393.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s cost effective to make and\nrelatively cheap to buy.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "394.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It picks up products, dust,\nand dirt and traps the", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "397.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "particles inside, safely\nprotecting", 
            "dur": "1.96", 
            "start": "400.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the paint from scratches.", 
            "dur": "1.4", 
            "start": "402.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And finally, they&#39;re extremely\ndurable and can be safely", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "403.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "cleaned in a washing machine.", 
            "dur": "2.17", 
            "start": "406.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Microfiber comes in many\ndifferent sizes and densities,", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "408.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "measured as grams per square\nmeter, or GSM for short.", 
            "dur": "3.36", 
            "start": "411.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "GSM can range from roughly 200\nto 600, but the optimal weight", 
            "dur": "3.77", 
            "start": "414.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for me is 300 GSM.", 
            "dur": "1.96", 
            "start": "418.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This insures the durability of\nthe towel without sacrificing", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "420.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "its pick up ability.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "423.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So those are my top five tools\nfor perfect paint.", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
